{"tid":2450302,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緬甸警察兄弟被捕 仍不忘舉抗爭手勢","createTime":"2021-03-17T09:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T10:34:01.000Z","uid":228441,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"706f69efc252988686f91118766ac1a71e1eb2ef","tid":2450302,"uid":228441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuSn4zk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuSn4zk.jpg&h=597affb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrom voice of Myanmar<br />\n<br />\n兩名警察兄弟被判入獄一年<br />\n<br />\nU Thant Sin, Kyan Khin 兩兄弟在緬甸任職警察，因參與反軍政府示威被捕，被判處監禁一年，被捕時仍不忘舉起抗爭手勢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港個班真係世界級垃圾 生生世世做支國人啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53647e14716066ebf510981e041a06ce067b64c9","tid":2450302,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:44:27.000Z","msg":"其實漢民族好撚現實<br />\n<br />\n有錢有權就會去賣命"},{"pid":"d0ed89d9c159de3e3ea4a8699c72a050984771b1","tid":2450302,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895bb03041af8b877ece2d8fe0efab7313d3064f","tid":2450302,"uid":228441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"補link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/123271498274532/posts/813397725928569/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F123271498274532%2Fposts%2F813397725928569%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F